Distribution. Eastern Australia , from VIC to northern QLD, but most common in the southern part of the range.

Biology. Collected by various means but apparently feeding on the soft-bodied, gilled basidiomes (mushrooms) of various Hymenomycetes, including a
Pleurotus
and an orange-gilled mushroom.
